# NAME: TikTok
# AUTHOR: guliaev/Rules
# SOURCES:
# - https://developers.tiktok.com/
# - https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community/blob/master/data/tiktok
# - https://github.com/blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script/blob/master/rule/Shadowrocket/TikTok/TikTok.list
# - https://github.com/M4jx/TikTokBlockList
# - https://bgp.tools/as/138699
# UPDATED: 2026-07-17
# NOTE: Only TikTok-owned AS138699 prefixes are included. Shared Akamai, Google, broad ByteDance AS396986, and unrelated ByteDance services are intentionally omitted.

# --- Core TikTok domains and API ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,musical.ly
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tik-tokapi.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktok.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokapis.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokd.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokd.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokv.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokv.eu
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokv.us
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokw.eu
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokw.us
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ttapis.com

